name: Variant
description:
Generative abstract painting, based on analog textures, hybrid, feedback loop, and made with code. 
Inspired by life, nature, to celebrate diversity, and the spirit of art is evolving. 

* Interactive feature :
Refresh/reload the page to get new variations.
